                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2002-12-15</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Having visited the region where this book is set I found it mostly interesting for giving a picture of how things used to be there - they are much changed today!<BR>For those who haven't been to the Asmat region of New Guinea, this will be a fascinating read. Those inspired to go should be prepared to find it a lot more civilized these days.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">outrageous but true account of life among headhunters</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
